1954;;Meet Mr. Callaghan;;British;;Charles Saunders;;Derrick De Marney, Harriette Johns;;crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meet_Mr._Callaghan;;Down at heel private Detective Slim Callaghan (Derrick De Marney) is hired by young socialite Cynthis Meraulton (Harriette Johns) to investigate. When her rich stepfather changes his will in her favour, and is then subsequently murdered, suspicion falls on Cynthia.